# API Endpoints — Authentication

Include the following auth endpoints:

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | /api/auth/signup | Register a new admin |
| POST | /api/auth/login | Login with Remember Me support |
| POST | /api/auth/logout | Invalidate session / refresh token |
| POST | /api/auth/refresh-token | Issue new access token using refresh token |
| POST | /api/auth/forgot-password | Send password reset email |
| POST | /api/auth/reset-password | Reset password via token |

